RDF Coder API

Other Packages 
Package Description
com.asemantics.rdfcoder
This package contains the CommandLine access point and the High Level API interface ( RDFCoder ).
com.asemantics.rdfcoder.inspector
This package provides methods to inspect the Code Model.
com.asemantics.rdfcoder.model
This package defines the RDF Code Model and the query facilities.
com.asemantics.rdfcoder.model.java
This package provides the model for the Java profile.
com.asemantics.rdfcoder.model.ontology
This package defines a basic ontology validator.
com.asemantics.rdfcoder.parser
This package defines a set of parser interfaces and implementations.
com.asemantics.rdfcoder.parser.bytecode
Bytecode based parser.
com.asemantics.rdfcoder.parser.javacc
JavaCC based parser.
com.asemantics.rdfcoder.parser.javadoc
Javadoc API based parser.
com.asemantics.rdfcoder.profile
This package defines a language Profile.
com.asemantics.rdfcoder.repository
This package defines utility classes to handle a file system repository able to store and organize the library data.
com.asemantics.rdfcoder.storage
This package defines a Code Model database.
